definitions.definition: A mentally unbalanced , unpredictable person, especially one who displays aggressive behavior .
A genetic sequence that inhibits terminal branching of the trachea and regulates dendrite pruning.

main_definition: ( informal , derogatory , countable ) A mentally unbalanced , unpredictable person, especially one who displays aggressive behavior .
secondary_definitions: ( genetics , uncountable ) A genetic sequence that inhibits terminal branching of the trachea and regulates dendrite pruning.
